### Optimization Category
- **Primary:** IO_BOUND (scan optimization)
- **Secondary:** Storage/indexing (zone-map usage)
- **Technique:** Block-level predicate pushdown with zone maps

The optimization leverages the fact that data is naturally clustered by orderdate (sorted on disk), making zone maps extremely effective for date range filtering. This is a classic plan-level optimization that reduces the physical I/O and CPU work by 70-80% for this specific bottleneck.